                "type": "stat_block_section",
                "subtype": "special_ability",
                "text": "A Stewards constable can wield manacles as though they were a one-handed basic melee weapon with the analog special property. If a manacles attack result would equal or exceed the target\u2019s KAC + 4, the constable can attempt a grapple combat maneuver against the target as part of the attack. If the attack result equals or exceeds the target\u2019s KAC + 13 and the combat maneuver check succeeds, the constable grapples and applies the restraints to the target.",
